### ============================================
### 🧪 TEST PURCHASE ORDERS API - SuperMarketMini
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminToken = 
@managerToken = 
@warehouseToken = 

### ============================================
### 🔐 1. LOGIN (Chạy trước để lấy token)
### ============================================

### 1.1 Login Admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### 1.2 Login Manager
# @name loginManager
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "manager",
  "password": "Manager@123"
}

### ============================================
### 📋 2. GET ALL PURCHASE ORDERS
### ============================================

### 2.1 Admin - Get All POs (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.2 Admin - Get POs with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.3 Admin - Filter by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders?status=DRAFT
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.4 Admin - Filter by Supplier
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders?supplierId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.5 Admin - Filter by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders?fromDate=2024-01-01&toDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.6 No Token - Get POs (Expected: 401 Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders

### ============================================
### 🔍 3. GET PURCHASE ORDER BY ID
### ============================================

### 3.1 Admin - Get PO by ID (Expected: 200 OK or 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3.2 Admin - Get Non-existent PO (Expected: 404 Not Found)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### ➕ 4. CREATE PURCHASE ORDER
### ============================================

### 4.1 Admin - Create PO Success (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "supplierId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 10,
      "unitCost": 100000
    },
    {
      "productId": 2,
      "quantity": 5,
      "unitCost": 200000
    }
  ],
  "note": "Đơn đặt hàng test"
}

### 4.2 Admin - Create PO without Supplier (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 10,
      "unitCost": 100000
    }
  ]
}

### 4.3 Admin - Create PO with Invalid Supplier (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "supplierId": 99999,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 10,
      "unitCost": 100000
    }
  ]
}

### 4.4 Admin - Create PO with Invalid Product (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "supplierId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 99999,
      "quantity": 10,
      "unitCost": 100000
    }
  ]
}

### 4.5 Admin - Create PO with Zero Quantity (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "supplierId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 0,
      "unitCost": 100000
    }
  ]
}

### 4.6 Admin - Create PO without Items (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "supplierId": 1,
  "items": []
}

### ============================================
### ✏️ 5. UPDATE PURCHASE ORDER
### ============================================

### 5.1 Admin - Update PO Note (Expected: 200 OK - chỉ khi DRAFT)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "note": "Ghi chú đã cập nhật"
}

### 5.2 Admin - Update Non-existent PO (Expected: 404 Not Found)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/99999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "note": "Test"
}

### 5.3 Admin - Update PO not in DRAFT (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "note": "Cannot update"
}

### ============================================
### 📤 6. SEND PURCHASE ORDER
### ============================================

### 6.1 Admin - Send PO (Expected: 200 OK - chuyển từ DRAFT sang ORDERED)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/1/send
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6.2 Admin - Send Non-existent PO (Expected: 404 Not Found)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/99999/send
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6.3 Admin - Send PO not in DRAFT (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/2/send
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 📥 7. RECEIVE PURCHASE ORDER
### ============================================

### 7.1 Admin - Receive PO (Expected: 200 OK - chuyển từ ORDERED sang RECEIVED)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/2/receive
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "note": "Nhận hàng đầy đủ"
}

### 7.2 Admin - Receive Non-existent PO (Expected: 404 Not Found)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/99999/receive
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7.3 Admin - Receive PO not in ORDERED (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/1/receive
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### ❌ 8. CANCEL PURCHASE ORDER
### ============================================

### 8.1 Admin - Cancel PO (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/3/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "reason": "Hủy do không còn nhu cầu"
}

### 8.2 Admin - Cancel Non-existent PO (Expected: 404 Not Found)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/99999/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8.3 Admin - Cancel Already Cancelled PO (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/3/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8.4 Admin - Cancel Received PO (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/2/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 🗑️ 9. DELETE PURCHASE ORDER
### ============================================

### 9.1 Admin - Delete DRAFT PO (Expected: 200 OK)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/4
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9.2 Admin - Delete CANCELLED PO (Expected: 200 OK)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9.3 Admin - Delete Non-DRAFT PO (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9.4 Admin - Delete Non-existent PO (Expected: 404 Not Found)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 📦 10. MANAGE PO ITEMS
### ============================================

### 10.1 Admin - Add Item to PO (Expected: 200 OK - chỉ khi DRAFT)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/1/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "productId": 3,
  "quantity": 15,
  "unitCost": 150000
}

### 10.2 Admin - Add Item to Non-DRAFT PO (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/2/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "productId": 3,
  "quantity": 15,
  "unitCost": 150000
}

### 10.3 Admin - Remove Item from PO (Expected: 200 OK - chỉ khi DRAFT)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/1/items/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 10.4 Admin - Remove Item from Non-DRAFT PO (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/purchaseorders/2/items/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 📝 HƯỚNG DẪN SỬ DỤNG
### ============================================
### 
### 1. Cài đặt VS Code extension "REST Client"
### 2. Chạy các request Login đầu tiên để lấy token
### 3. Copy token vào biến tương ứng
### 4. Chạy các request test theo thứ tự
###
### WORKFLOW TEST:
### 1. Create PO (DRAFT) → 2. Add Items → 3. Send PO (ORDERED)
### 4. Receive PO (RECEIVED) → Kiểm tra kho được cập nhật
###
### ============================================
### ✅ CHECKLIST TEST
### ============================================
###
### GET ALL:
### [ ] Get all POs → 200 OK
### [ ] Get with pagination → 200 OK
### [ ] Filter by status → 200 OK
### [ ] Filter by supplier → 200 OK
### [ ] Filter by date → 200 OK
###
### GET BY ID:
### [ ] Get existing PO → 200 OK
### [ ] Get non-existent → 404 Not Found
###
### CREATE:
### [ ] Create valid PO → 200 OK
### [ ] Create without supplier → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Create invalid supplier → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Create invalid product → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Create zero quantity → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Create without items → 400 Bad Request
###
### UPDATE:
### [ ] Update PO note → 200 OK
### [ ] Update non-existent → 404 Not Found
### [ ] Update non-DRAFT → 400 Bad Request
###
### SEND:
### [ ] Send DRAFT PO → 200 OK
### [ ] Send non-existent → 404 Not Found
### [ ] Send non-DRAFT → 400 Bad Request
###
### RECEIVE:
### [ ] Receive ORDERED PO → 200 OK
### [ ] Receive non-existent → 404 Not Found
### [ ] Receive non-ORDERED → 400 Bad Request
###
### CANCEL:
### [ ] Cancel PO → 200 OK
### [ ] Cancel non-existent → 404 Not Found
### [ ] Cancel already cancelled → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Cancel received → 400 Bad Request
###
### DELETE:
### [ ] Delete DRAFT → 200 OK
### [ ] Delete CANCELLED → 200 OK
### [ ] Delete non-DRAFT → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Delete non-existent → 404 Not Found
###
### ITEMS:
### [ ] Add item to DRAFT → 200 OK
### [ ] Add to non-DRAFT → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Remove item from DRAFT → 200 OK
### [ ] Remove from non-DRAFT → 400 Bad Request
###